==Related resources==
This book is narrowly focused on a handful of results that are directly useful for understanding 0.999.... It omits plenty of topics that are essential for a balanced understanding of calculus and real analysis. For Wikibooks that develop a broader background, see:
*[[Real Analysis]] and other books in [[:Category:Mathematical analysis]]
*[[Calculus]] and other books in [[:Category:Calculus]]

There are also independent learning activities and materials in these areas at [[Wikiversity:Wikiversity:What is Wikiversity?|Wikiversity]]:
*[[Wikiversity:Topic:Real analysis|Topic:Real analysis]]
*[[Wikiversity:Topic:Calculus|Topic:Calculus]]

For an encyclopedic overview of 0.999..., including history, education, applications, and popular culture, see [[Wikipedia:Wikipedia:About|Wikipedia]]:
*[[Wikipedia:0.999...|0.999...]]

